CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 3, 1973, pg. 1 reads:"Homecoming Queen - Miss Gail Minor, the first Black Homecoming Queen in Pitt history, rides in parade with Chancellor Wesley W. Posvar. (Photo by Teenie Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Four women holding roses seated in back of convertible, with University of Pittsburgh mascot, in homecoming parade in front of Cathedral of Learning, University of Pittsburgh
